        {
            "_id": "HOIGg1GjZy5R358W",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/TwoActions.webp",
            "name": "Barbed Net Barrage",
            "sort": 500000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The battalion hurls barbed nets. This barrage is a @Template[type:burst|distance:10] within 30 feet that deals @Damage[6d8[slashing]|options:area-damage] damage with a @Check[reflex|dc:37|traits:magical,unholy] save. A creature can [[/act escape dc=37]] from the penalties imposed by these nets, but each Escape attempt deals @Damage[3d6[slashing]|options:area-damage] damage to the creature from the nets' barbs, regardless of whether the attempt succeeds. When the levaloch battalion is reduced to 2 segments, this area decreases to a @Template[type:burst|distance:5].</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature takes no damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes half damage and takes a –5-foot circumstance penalty to its Speeds until it Escapes.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes full damage, is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Clumsy]{Clumsy 1}, and takes a –10-foot circumstance penalty to its Speeds until it Escapes.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature takes double damage, is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Clumsy]{Clumsy 2}, and is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Immobilized] until it Escapes.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
                    "value": [
                        "magical",
                        "unholy"
                    ]
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        },
        {
            "_id": "rOoWVnQC0r8nJ53z",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneThreeActions.webp",
            "name": "Merciless Tridents",
            "sort": 600000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The levalochs make coordinated melee attacks with their tridents. Each enemy within a @Template[type:emanation|distance:5] must attempt a @Check[reflex|dc:37|basic|traits:magical,unholy] save. The damage depends on the number of actions.</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> @Damage[2d8[piercing]|options:area-damage] damage plus vicious cruelty</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> @Damage[(4d8+10)[piercing]|options:area-damage] damage plus vicious cruelty</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span> @Damage[(6d8+12)[piercing]|options:area-damage] damage plus vicious cruelty</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
